24:43.888 --> 24:52.982
after him because he was too conventional. So the 
trick today is, if you're running a university

24:53.502 --> 25:15.469
press, is you've got to be financially 
responsible, and you've got to accomplish what

24:53.502 --> 25:15.469
universities expect university presses to do, 
which is to contribute to scholarship, enhance

24:53.502 --> 25:15.469
the reputation of the university, keep the 
faculty happy. So doing that today is tougher than

25:15.489 --> 25:22.598
it has ever been.

25:22.932 --> 25:24.634
