people who are publishing saleable books, like

25:25.095 --> 25:30.461
regional books and trade books, those books are 
being returned. The superstores now are buying

25:30.601 --> 25:38.371
these books in great quantities, but they're 
returning them in even greater quantities. Oh, I

25:38.411 --> 25:38.992
know. They are. I know. I've personally 
experienced that. Yeah. So the trick is you need to

25:42.456 --> 25:51.387
publish, in my view, a variety of books. You can't 
just do regional books. You can't just do

25:53.774 --> 25:56.197
scholarly monographs. You've got to do 
textbooks, professional books, reference

25:56.217 --> 26:02.384
books, and electronic things as well. And you've 
